#

Penne alla Vodka

30 min
$12.99
550 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Main

Tags:

ItalianPastaComfort Food

Description

Creamy, tangy, and full of flavor, this Penne alla Vodka is a comforting dish that's easy to prepare.

Ingredients

  • penne pasta: 8 oz
  • vodka: 1/2 cup
  • heavy cream: 1 cup
  • crushed tomatoes: 1 cup
  • parmesan cheese: 1/2 cup, grated
  • butter: 2 tbsp
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • onion: 1 small, diced
  • fresh basil: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • red pepper flakes: 1/2 tsp
